pulses.name: 20250124 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
24 Jan 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - The US is a significant source of cyber activities, with numerous instances of attacks including Back Orifice traffic and various botnet activities such as SystemBC.
- China (CN) - China is notable for its involvement in multiple attacks, particularly targeting Zivif PR115-204-P-RS web cameras with hardcoded passwords and various unauthorized access vulnerabilities.
- India (IN) - India has shown a high frequency of attacks, primarily involving NETGEAR DGN1000 CGI unauthenticated remote code execution and D-Link devices, indicating vulnerabilities in widely used network devices.
